name: Vibe with Chakras
description:
Unlock the parallel universe with your inner Chakras
Meditation = Key
  7 Chakras
From Top
1.Crown Chakra - To enlighten spiritual connection of one individual to others and the supreme beings.
2.Third Eye Chakra - To enable telepathic abilities and increased focus.
3.Throat Chakra - To improve the spiritual, communicational and artistic abilities in our body.
4.Heart Chakra - The source place of affection and relationships. It is believed to bring wholeness into life.
5.Solar Plexus Chakra - The chakra of inner power, joy, success, charge, confidence, warmness and energy.
6.Sacral Chakra - Chakra responsible for creativity, sexuality, desire, compassion and reproductive system
7.Root Chakra - It is crucial chakra which defines an individual's relation to the earth, which leads to impact on vitality, passion, survival, wealth, courage, power, strength and war.
